messages.title:
Increase productivity of your teams
and ensure the security of your data
messages.card.user.title: Advanced management of users
messages.card.user.content: Easily manage your employees, external partners as well as the security and access of your products. The kSuite dashboard allows you to control all aspects of your business from a single place.
messages.card.team.title: Teams management
messages.card.team.content: Create work teams with specific rights and access to facilitate the management of your employees. kSuite simplifies and speeds up all your personnel movement management.
messages.card.calendar.title: Calendars and shared addresses
messages.card.calendar.content: Create work teams with specific rights and access to facilitate the management of your employees. kSuite simplifies and speeds up all your personnel movement management.
